::Cygnar::
       "Ah, just one more thing.  When, you fight Galvatron, only one of you 
must walk away.  Do I make myself clear?  Only one of you..."  He nods 
gravely.  I bid you farewell ... for now."  He turns and nods to his escort.  
"Well, then, let us be off."

--part1_12a.156ff6f9.2a848b80_boundary
